CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIs there a vaccine for meningitis, and
OL,12,Fhow do I know if I've had one?
OL,14,FSeveral vaccines protect against
OL,15,Fdifferent meningococcal groups,
OL,16,Fincluding MenB and MenACWY. Other
OL,17,Froutine childhood vaccines, such as
OL,18,Fthe 6-in-1 vaccine and MMR, protect
OL,19,Fagainst infections that can also cause
OL,20,Fmeningitis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FThe pneumococcal vaccine is offered to
OL,7,Fbabies in two doses or a single dose
OL,8,Fto adults aged 65 or over.
OL,10,FTeenagers, sixth formers and freshers
OL,11,Fattending university for the first
OL,12,Ftime can have the MenACWY vaccine,
OL,13,Fwhich can help protect against
OL,14,Fmeningitis and sepsis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,F"Vaccination remains the best
OL,7,Fprotection. The MenACWY and MenB
OL,8,Fvaccines used in the UK are safe,
OL,9,Fwelltested, and available free to
OL,10,Feligible UK and international
OL,11,Fstudents," said Dr Simon Clarke,
OL,12,FAssociate Professor of Cellular
OL,13,FMicrobiology, University of Reading.
OL,15,FThe MenACWY vaccine can be given up to
OL,16,Fthe age of 25 if it has been missed
OL,17,Fand is also available to some
OL,18,Findividuals who are at greater risk
OL,19,Fdue to a medical condition, work,
OL,20,Ftravel or close contact with someone
OL,21,Fwho is infected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FWhile the NHS offers vaccinations to
OL,7,Fthose most at risk, private
OL,8,Fvaccinations are available at some
OL,9,Ftravel clinics, private GP practices
OL,10,Fand pharmacies.
OL,12,FFor the particular strain identified
OL,13,Fin the Kent outbreak, the MenB vaccine
OL,14,Fis the best protection.
OL,16,FHowever, as Dr Alfahl says: "many
OL,17,Fcurrent university students were born
OL,18,Fbefore the infant MenB programme began
OL,19,Fin 2015, which means some of them may
OL,20,Fnever have been routinely offered that
OL,21,Fvaccine."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FIf you are unsure if you or your child
OL,7,Fhas been vaccinated, you can speak to
OL,8,Fyour GP.
OL,10,FShould I be getting the MenB vaccine?
OL,12,FThe government are not currently
OL,13,Fadvising people to pay for private
OL,14,Fvaccinations.
OL,16,FThe MenB vaccine is offered by some
OL,17,Fprivate pharmacies; however, they are
OL,18,Fwarning of shortages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FSpeaking on Good Morning Britain on
OL,7,FWednesday, UK health secretary Wes
OL,8,FStreeting said that this was only a
OL,9,Ftemporary supply issue, and that there
OL,10,Fare 'plenty' of meningitis jabs in the
OL,11,FUK.
OL,13,FFrom Wednesday, 5,000 students in
OL,14,Fhalls at Kent University will be able
OL,15,Fto access MenB vaccines in a targeted
OL,16,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FOn the prospect of a wider, national
OL,7,FNHS vaccine roll-out, Streeting said:
OL,8,F"We are going to approach that in an
OL,9,Fevidence-based way, I don't want to do
OL,10,Fthat in a knee-jerk way."
OL,12,FStreeting said that the government is
OL,13,Fcurrently seeking advice from the
OL,14,FJCVI, an independent body of
OL,15,Fscientists who make recommendations to
OL,16,Fgovernment, to look at what has
OL,17,Fhappened in Canterbury and issue fresh
OL,18,Fadvice.
OL,20,FWhat other ways can I help protect
OL,21,Fmyself from meningitis?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FAvoid sharing items which come into
OL,7,Fcontact with your mouth, such as food
OL,8,Fand eating utensils.
OL,10,FDrinks and vapes are also best kept to
OL,11,Fone person to help prevent spread.
OL,13,FFollowing the recent outbreak, GPs
OL,14,Facross the country have now been told
OL,15,Fto prescribe antibiotics to anyone who
OL,16,Fvisited a nightclub in Canterbury from
OL,17,FMarch 5-7, plus students from the
OL,18,FUniversity of Kent.
OL,20,FWhat further measures are being taken
OL,21,Fin Kent?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency and the
OL,7,FNHS have provided antibiotics for some
OL,8,Fstudents at the University of Kent,
OL,9,Ffollowing the outbreak there.
OL,11,FTrish Mannes, UKHSA regional deputy
OL,12,Fdirector for the South East, said:
OL,13,F"Students and staff will
OL,14,Funderstandably be feeling worried
OL,15,Fabout the risk of further cases;
OL,16,Fhowever, we would like to reassure
OL,17,Fthem that close contacts of cases have
OL,18,Fbeen given antibiotics as a
OL,19,Fprecautionary measure."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31121
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FVaccines are now also available to a
OL,7,Fselect cohort of students living in
OL,8,Fshared university accommodation.
OL,10,FYou can read more about the advice
OL,11,Fissued to University of Kent students
OL,12,Fhere, and for school children here.
OL,14,FHow is meningitis treated?
OL,16,FPeople with suspected meningitis may
OL,17,Fhave to have hospital tests to get a
OL,18,Fdiagnosis and find out if their
OL,19,Fillness is a viral or bacterial
OL,20,Finfection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
