OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FBacterial meningitis usually requires
OL,7,Fhospital treatment for at least a
OL,8,Fweek, including antibiotics, fluids
OL,9,Fand oxygen.
OL,11,FShould students be especially careful?
OL,13,FAccess to vaccinations has meant
OL,14,Foutbreaks are more unusual; however,
OL,15,Fmeningitis can spread rapidly in
OL,16,Fplaces like universities and colleges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/25
