OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773864688
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,F"That's why it's vital that, if a
OL,7,Ffriend goes to bed unwell, you check
OL,8,Fon them regularly and don't hesitate
OL,9,Fto seek medical help by contacting
OL,10,Ftheir GP or calling NHS 111 if they
OL,11,Fhave these symptoms or you're
OL,12,Fconcerned about them. This could save
OL,13,Ftheir life."
OL,15,FNHS advice to students is to make sure
OL,16,Ftheir vaccinations are up to date
OL,17,Fbefore starting university or college,
OL,18,Fincluding the MenACWY vaccine and both
OL,19,Fdoses of the MMR vaccine.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@LO]
